{"tid":886812,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"兩份工點簡好","createTime":"2018-11-02T11:44:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T07:08:18.000Z","uid":17189,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2d284cab510c8dc882ed576f0fd97780c8655745","tid":886812,"uid":17189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:44:04.000Z","msg":"第一份工好近屋企<br />\n講緊係近到出門搭兩個站地鐵加埋都唔洗十五分鐘<br />\n講真真係好吸引<br />\n除左食野平 車錢時間都慳唔小 老闆又好好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第二份工人工多成6K<br />\n港島區<br />\n仲要做阿大<br />\n但番工車程都要超過一個鐘<br />\n車費食飯都多第一份工成2K<br />\n<br />\n其實第一份工雖然未算阿大<br />\n但都話得事<br />\n<br />\n宜家仲做緊第一份工<br />\n好順利<br />\n但編編哩個時候就突然收到第二個offer<br />\n點點我人生成日都係咁<br />\n編編最順利既時候都出現考驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8514525aaf87540bcf6c33eb01cba9eb0050a06e","tid":886812,"uid":30578,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:45:43.000Z","msg":"6k wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa5f8b1869ca1091ac0fe8b7bf62fca6de121112","tid":886812,"uid":40303,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:46:47.000Z","msg":"第一個啦 少幾k換返多啲自由時間 更何況第2個都有可能係伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"607f83f256465e376994fb7bc9daa3b732c06282","tid":886812,"uid":17189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa5f8b1869ca1091ac0fe8b7bf62fca6de121112","tid":886812,"uid":40303,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:46:47.000Z","msg":"第一個啦 少幾k換返多啲自由時間 更何況第2個都有可能係伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:47:09.000Z","msg":"我都有咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"995d9133a50dee8d2e5cd53f85de3eb7f3b533e3","tid":886812,"uid":111996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:47:45.000Z","msg":"時間是金錢<br />\n時間重要 就一<br />\n如果時間可以換更多金錢也可考慮<br />\n畢竟 你做一 假如ot,或做其他炒散,都未必搵到咁多錢<br />\n係我就做二<br />\n但如果你怕辛苦又性，寧願你做一，起碼穩定<br />\n因為做二怕你做得唔開心 到時又唔做 有一個月無野做 無收野<br />\n行申9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad7c5ca6ead794e4144d544c64759cf81f3f6ef","tid":886812,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:48:13.000Z","msg":"另一間個阿頭西唔西都好緊要"},{"pid":"faf96c5b715ea913eeb388caadfbf4d86ce8ed84","tid":886812,"uid":19979,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:53:03.000Z","msg":"第二份 做管理層前途好d"},{"pid":"c5480a89a1d80ec16497948b8d36cd5f744ce2ea","tid":886812,"uid":219263,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T12:04:49.000Z","msg":"第二 <br />\n我覺得似係個天俾個機會你轉下/升職<br />\n返工太近屋企其實好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51372e145bc0e63f8deaf59f8628bb3b18da0009","tid":886812,"uid":76753,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T13:31:08.000Z","msg":"本身搵幾多先<br />\n100k多6k, 同10k多6k係兩回事"},{"pid":"ff824a26ee2cf88d28b3c234dd98fc4e7144bc3d","tid":886812,"uid":84382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51372e145bc0e63f8deaf59f8628bb3b18da0009","tid":886812,"uid":76753,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T13:31:08.000Z","msg":"本身搵幾多先<br />\n100k多6k, 同10k多6k係兩回事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T05:33:54.000Z","msg":"正想咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4f15cdd43c9db06e4ab04ab5a50f23be9849556","tid":886812,"uid":75692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T06:00:34.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"23f1e23f58a18fcac1bfca2f97315743152665d4","tid":886812,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T06:47:40.000Z","msg":"第2份啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff7e3e3737977e537ef5f6d8ecd84dd9fa75cd6","tid":886812,"uid":188493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy